com.joliciel.talismane.machineLearning

Interface MachineLearningModel

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    ClassificationModel, OpenNLPModel
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractMachineLearningModel, LinearSVMModel, LinearSVMOneVsRestModel, MaximumEntropyModel, PerceptronClassificationModel

    public interface MachineLearningModel
    A machine learning model, capable of providing a DecisionMaker, and encapsluating all of the information required to analyse mew data (e.g. feature descriptors).
    Author:
    Assaf Urieli
